HOW IT WORKS

The new standard for checking

1. Sign up

Book a demo with a Zinc and we can recommend the best checks for you. Or create an account and connect Zinc to your ATS.

2. Request checks

Request checks at the click of a button directly from your ATS. Automated email/SMS reminders mean speedy responses.

3. Let Zinc work

Zinc collects checks from previous employers and government bodies, then analyses your check data and delivers your report.

Is checking painful?

Reference and background checking has been painful, time-consuming and slow for too long. Screening candidates often involves downloading, printing and constant chasing which rarely uncovers anything actionable.

Implement Zinc

Zinc helps talent teams update their checking processes to a modern solution that's inline with your employer brand. We'll remove your unnecessary admin and deliver you reports with clear candidate insights, fast.
